Although there is still some error, it is not significant; the screenshot might be slightly skewed.

= Next Steps

From the image, we can see that I used a *small arrow* to represent the player's character. Intuitively, the direction of the arrow should align with the character's orientation, but currently, there is no related logic, so the arrow always points to the left. In the next step, we will implement this logic to make the character's state on the webpage look more complete.
